[The above are several excerpts from the exhaustive article, selected in accordance with their relevance to the animal reservoir aspect of MERS-CoV. Bats' potential role is addressed in the article as well. Subscribers are encouraged to read the full text of Cynthia Gorney's article, which makes excellent reading. - Mod.AS]

